8. Jwt_Secret,Jwt_Expires Variables Added In ENV File

9. 2)In Jwtmodule add inject,useFactory inside that secret,signinoptions will be added

10. Next, In AuthService adding signup function in that creating jwt token,saving user _id in that token.

11. Signup,Login DTO Added.